{"tid":1218261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「你哋為我地做咗咩，我地知嫁！」","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:29:41.000Z","uid":112643,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6311ae0f29c0ecd05402e1afa573d371ca97a52","tid":1218261,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"我尋晚發夢，夢見自己尋日去狗公園撚狗撚咗十幾個鐘，無嘢落個肚，夜晚終於有時間食碗麵。坐入鋪頭嗌咗碗雲吞麵，就算手手腳腳紅晒，俾火燒咁都理唔得咁多，食咗碗麵先算。食完碗麵，埋單嗰陣老細講咗句：「唔洗啦後生仔，你哋為我地做咗咩，我地知嫁！翻去好好休息啦。」<br />\n<br />\n我當堂流咗幾滴馬尿，嗰只係想講翻句「香港人，加油」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eae3677903c54e8244cd843d0a6e7089368b7a0","tid":1218261,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:25:16.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1215781/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1215781/page/3</a> <br />\n醫院係要保護病人私隱<br />\n求求大家幫幫手 等受傷人士可以放心睇醫生<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"1434829adde74215bac1b94288e4fe907c1743de","tid":1218261,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"491708c2455e0ee59e5f6786b493db9af3903a75","tid":1218261,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}